original: Your wretch of a former regent that saw you imprisoned on charges of insanity no longer wields any influence at court. The new regent has released you.
translation: 借口精神失常把你关押起来的前摄政者在宫廷中已不再具有影响力。新摄政者释放了你。

original: Not a moment too soon.
translation: 太晚了。

original: Watch out, world! Here I come!
translation: 小心，全世界！我来了！

original: You have successfully thwarted your opponent's designs on your regency, and can continue to serve at the pleasure of [Root.Liege.GetTitledFirstName].
translation: 你成功挫败了对手夺取摄政地位的企图，可以继续侍奉[Root.Liege.GetTitledFirstName]了。

original: Like the spineless coward [From.GetSheHe] is, [From.GetTitledFirstName] has refused to rise to your challenge!
translation: [From.GetTitledFirstName]拒绝接受你的挑战，[From.GetSheHe]真是个没种的懦夫！

original: Milksop! Worm!
translation: 懦夫！胆小鬼！

original: In a desperate effort to save [From.GetHerHis] skin, [From.GetTitledFirstName] has decided to abdicate the position of regent to you.
translation: 眼见逃脱无望，[From.GetTitledFirstName]决定将摄政的位置让给你。

original: Well, that was easy.
translation: 这很容易。

original: The blood of your opponent seeps into the ground as you lean on your sword to catch your breath. It was a brief and violent struggle, but the poor fool lies maimed at your feet, clinging pitifully to life. The day is yours.
translation: 对手的鲜血在地面流淌，你则倚靠在剑上喘气.这是场短暂而激烈的战斗，不过那个可怜的蠢货现在正遍体鳞伤地趴在你的脚边，可怜地挣扎着。胜利属于你！

original: The blood of your opponent seeps into the ground as you lean on your sword to catch your breath. It was a brief and violent struggle, but the poor fool lies dead at your feet.
translation: 对手的鲜血在地面流淌，你则倚靠在剑上喘气。这是场短暂而激烈的战斗，不过那个可怜的蠢货最终还是在你的脚边死去了。

original: [Root.Regent.GetFirstName] stabs wildly in the air with [Root.Regent.GetHerHis] dagger, missing you by a hair's breadth as you leap away in panic. Guards rush inside and pull your regent away as [Root.Regent.GetSheHe] screams, "Why won't you die?!"
translation: [Root.Regent.GetFirstName]用[Root.Regent.GetHerHis]匕首狠狠地刺过来，千钧一发之际，你险些没有躲开。卫兵迅速冲进来，制服了你的摄政者。[Root.Regent.GetSheHe]尖声叫着，「你怎么还不死？！」

original: Thrown into a dark cell.
translation: 被关入地牢。

original: Yearly income less than
translation: 年收入少于

original: Yearly income greater than
translation: 年收入多于

original: Landed title changes de jure liege
translation: 实地头衔的法理领主改变了

original: After §Y$YEARS$§! years under the §Y$NEW_LIEGE$§!, the §Y$TITLE$§! is now considered part of it.
translation: 经过§Y$NEW_LIEGE$§!长达§Y$YEARS$§!年的统治，§Y$TITLE$§!现在已成为其法理领土。

original: Cannot usurp religious head titles
translation: 不能篡夺宗教领袖的头衔

original: §Y[Actor.GetTitledFirstName]§! is not in revolt
translation: §Y[Actor.GetTitledFirstName]§!不在叛乱

original: §Y[Actor.GetTitledFirstName]§! is not a vassal of §Y[ThirdPartyCharacter.GetTitledFirstName]§!
translation: §Y[Actor.GetTitledFirstName]§!不是§Y[ThirdPartyCharacter.GetTitledFirstName]§!的封臣

original: §RBROKEN SAVEGAME§!
translation: §R存档损坏§!
